data.description: This beautiful 3 bed. 2 bath home was fully remodeled in 2023 from top to bottom; The Kitchen is amazing and tastefully done with modern style cabinets and quartz counter tops, all fresh new appliances all stay.  The gleaming hardwood floors through-out home are refinished and gorgeous. Fully remodeled bathrooms with Bluetooth fan for music. The Full un-finished basement is huge for extra space and future project. This home is absolutely amazing and gorgeous from the moment you step in, close to major shopping centers, and quiet location to call home.
